The APP looks up sunrise and sunset times based on the latitude and longitude entered by the user. The lat range is -90.00 to 90.00 and longitude range is -180.00 to 180.00. If it is greater than or less than the range, the APP will convert it to the correct number. Negative numbers represent south lat and west longitudes.
